}

docs {
  ## Get Preferences

  Returns all display/UI preferences. No parameters required.

  **Expected Response:**
  Object with key-value pairs, e.g.:
  ```json
  {
    "chartPalette": "default",
    "customColorBoth": "#4CAF50",
    "customColorIntro": "#2196F3",
    "customColorCredits": "#FF9800",
    "customColorNone": "#F44336",
    "tableGridlines": "true",
    "tableStripedRows": "true",
    "hideMovieLibraries": "false",
    "hideMixedLibraries": "false"
  }
  ```

  Returns empty object/defaults if no preferences have been saved.

  **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - ✅ Returns preferences object
  - ✅ Works even with no saved preferences (returns defaults)
  - ✅ Requires admin authentication
}
